OL,3,CFormer BA chief pilot to investigate
OL,4,CAurigny's reliability
OL,6,FA former British Airways chief pilot
OL,7,Fand a aviation financial expert will
OL,8,Flead an inquiry into Aurigny's
OL,9,Freliability as an airline.
OL,11,FThe investigation will focus on
OL,12,Fwhether the States-owned carrier can
OL,13,Fdeliver the resilient air links
OL,14,FGuernsey needs following months of
OL,15,Fdelays and cancellations.
OL,17,FThe States Trading Supervisory Board
OL,18,Fhas commissioned the inquiry and its
OL,19,Ffindings are expected within weeks.
