OL,3,CFormer BA chief pilot to investigate
OL,4,CAurigny's reliability
OL,6,FThe report will be created by two
OL,7,Fleading aviation experts, Captain Doug
OL,8,FBrown and Mark Elliott.
OL,10,FCaptain Brown was the Chief Pilot of
OL,11,FBritish Airways' Boeing fleet,
OL,12,Fresponsible for managing more than
OL,13,F1,800 pilots and 110 aircraft during
OL,14,Ffour decades at the company.
OL,16,FMr Elliott is an accountant and has
OL,17,Fhelped a number of European airlines
OL,18,Fthrough major efficiency savings - he
OL,19,Fhas extensive experience in buying and
OL,20,Fleasing aircraft.
